		   <span class="sm">Posted: Sep 27th  2004 at  5:37pm EDT<span class="notbold">| <span class="sm">IP: Logged</span> | <a class="sm" href="/db/classes.html?class=6;mid=1096321032602076369;num=4;page=1;post=1;replyto=1096321032602076369"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." height="11" width="17" /> Reply to this</a>    </span></span></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign="top" class="mform" ><span class="fs8"><span class="notbold">By: </span><a href="/db/poster.html?user=414927"><span class="">Niffurn</span></a><b><span class=""></span></b><br />1 posts
		   <br /><span class="nobr"><span class="notbold">Score</span>: Decent  </span><br />
<br/><a href="/db/classes.html?class=6;mid=1096321032602076369;page=1;howmany=50#1096321032602076369"><img alt="" title="Use this to create a link to this post" src="/shared/garrowrt.png" border="0" height="9" width="11" /> Link to this post</a>

