<td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%">
<p>Erudite Paladin, the real challenge.  <br /> <br />Yes, you can become quite powerful in the high end game. At the later points you can easily get gear to overcome your lousy starting abilities. It will be a difficult road at times, as your STR is so low. Usually tanks concentrate mostly on STA and AC, however, you will need to keep a close eye for STR as well so you can carry the heavy armor you need to wear.  Erudite pallies do have access to some unique items, though I don't know much about them other than that they are there. Try looking in the Quest section and you will probably be able to find some of the stuff. </p>
